</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="8.[264,1324,284,1230]" box="[312,900,1164,1190]" pageId="8" pageNumber="45">tibial apex with two spurs, as in most Apoderinae.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="8.[264,1324,284,1230]" box="[312,796,1204,1230]" pageId="8" pageNumber="45">venter slightly convex (concave in male).</paragraph>
